name: Metanoia Mixie Eggs
description:
Metanoia is an alternative nation native to web3, where everyone will be able to gain access and own a slice of the power and economic opportunities previously only made available to the political elite, the well connected or the rich. 

The Founding Citizen NFTs, represented in the form of Mixies, allows holders to get special perks and privileges from Metanoia. 
Learn more about Founding Citizen NFT benefits: https://medium.com/metanoia-country/founding-citizen-nft-sale-b7e1524a5e69
